/GCwidth {currentpoint stroke M dup Gwidth 2 div vshift R {ExtendTextBox} forall} def
/GLwidth2 {0 Gwidth AddGlyphWidth} def
/GRwidth2 {Gwidth -1 mul 0 AddGlyphWidth} def
